490
00:38:12,815 --> 00:38:15,608
a strange little smile on his face,

491
00:38:15,609 --> 00:38:18,229
watching us drink his beer.

492
00:38:24,452 --> 00:38:25,812
Hey...

493
00:38:26,078 --> 00:38:27,454
Want a cold one, Andy?

494
00:38:27,455 --> 00:38:29,115
No, thanks.

495
00:38:29,206 --> 00:38:31,346
I gave up drinking.

496
