497
00:38:38,090 --> 00:38:41,610
Or maybe make a few friends among us cons.

498
00:38:43,179 --> 00:38:47,059
Me, I think he did it just to feel normal again.

499
00:38:47,725 --> 00:38:50,285
If only for a short while.

500
00:38:52,688 --> 00:38:54,168
king me.

