00:42:16,350 --> 00:42:18,309
Take a few weeks.

542
00:42:18,310 --> 00:42:19,519
Weeks?

543
00:42:19,520 --> 00:42:24,857
Well, yeah, Andy. I don't have her stuffed down the front of my pants right now, I'm sorry to say.

544
00:42:24,858 --> 00:42:27,298
But I'll get her. Relax.

545
00:42:29,613 --> 00:42:31,033
Thanks.

546
00:42:31,198 --> 00:42:34,778
- It was a surprise, Mr. Farrell. - It was.

547
00:42:41,377 --> 00:42:43,277
[ON MOVIE SCREEN] 

548
00:42:44,545 --> 00:42:45,905
(Grunts) 

