00:42:56,464 --> 00:43:00,351
(Door closes as film dialogue continues) - Where's he going? - Grab his ankles. sit down. Did you tell him what I'm doing here? No, I wanted to save that as a surprise, too. Hang on to your hat, Mr. Farrell... - Take a walk. - I gotta change the reel. I said fuck off!

550
00:43:00,352 --> 00:43:02,732
Ain't you gonna scream?

551
00:43:04,523 --> 00:43:07,023
Let's get this over with.

552
00:43:10,446 --> 00:43:12,946
He broke my fuckin' nose!

553
00:43:22,583 --> 00:43:25,383
Now...I'm gonna open my fly...

