Andy spent a month in the infirmary.

574
00:44:30,651 --> 00:44:33,451
Bogs spent a week in the hole.

575
00:44:37,616 --> 00:44:39,576
Time's up, Bogs.

576
00:44:42,913 --> 00:44:45,233
It's your world, boss.

