725
00:55:54,459 --> 00:55:55,999
Sure can.

726
00:56:18,106 --> 00:56:24,488
He's a friend of yours, and Brooks is a reasonable man. But you write your letters, if it makes you happy. I'll even mail them for you. How's that? so, andy started writing a letter a week, just like he said. And, just like Norton said, Andy got no answers.

727
00:56:24,489 --> 00:56:29,989
The following April, Andy did tax returns for half the guards at Shawshank.

